casebody.data:
No. 111,

Orig.

Delaware v. New York.

Motions of Midwest Securities Trust Co. et al. and Securities Industries Association et al. for leave to file briefs as amici curiae granted. Motion of Delaware for leave to file a brief in reply to briefs of the Texas Group Intervenors granted. Motion of New York for leave to file a reply brief granted. Motion of Massachusetts for leave to file a complaint in intervention granted. Exceptions to the Report of the Special Master are set for oral argument in due course. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 504 U. S. 939.]
